	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />well it looks like the old breakout box was for looks only.  From what I found the eproms were interchangeable on a board in the display and the came carts were just window dressing.  The NES board was right next to the multi eprom board and was connected with what looks like a "flat" 72 pin for lack of a better description.
<br />
<br />I think I am just going to move the board and cart tray together to a different location so I don't have to extend the 72 pin.

		

		</td>
